title: Is The GOP Ready For A Midterm Courtroom Brawl? with Matt Schlapp and Robby Starbuck
itunes:title: Is The GOP Ready For A Midterm Courtroom Brawl? with Matt Schlapp and Robby Starbuck
description:
Republicans were totally unprepared to contest disputed elections in 2020. They didn't have lawyers and they didn't have a plan. Matt Schlapp joins Charlie to tell about how conservative campaigns have laid the legal groundwork to prevent the same calamity in 2022. Plus, Robby Starbuck joins to discuss the revelations of industrial-level censorship efforts by the Biden DHS.
